metadata.name: METAMORPHOSIS
metadata.description:
The details in the little things are sometimes the most splendid. Metamorphosis is a micro-texture from a larger painting which drew inspiration from the wings of a butterfly. I've always been intrigued by their color combinations, textures, and iridescence - each unique amongst over 17,500 species. 

This NFT comes paired with a 12x12" Framed Archival Print, signed and numbered 1/1. Free shipping included. 

Additionally, every NFT from this collection has additional utility:
- First look & early access to fine art drops
- Raffle entry for a quarterly NFT airdrop
- Free access to future art shows, both in-person and virtual
- Access to a private page on my website for NFT updates, behind the scenes, and more

This is a very special genesis collection kicking off my NFT journey and I appreciate every ounce of support!

xx
Courtney
